title: 230: Week 10 Preview, Northwestern's Godwin Igwebuike
itunes:title: 230: Week 10 Preview, Northwestern's Godwin Igwebuike
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks preview each NFL game in Week 10 (2:45) and discuss which players need to step it up (22:10). The guys are then joined by Northwestern safety Godwin Igwebuike (24:40) before they make this weekend's college picks (40:30).
